Figure 4. Comparison of Li anode swelling. Cross-sectional SEM images of cycled Li metals with (a) neat electrolyte (control) and (b–e) NDCEs (5, 10, 15, and 20 mg mL

 –1

). All samples were obtained after 80 cycles at 1 C-rate (1.5 mA cm

 –2

). (f) Thickness comparison of the passivation layer grown on Li anodes.

